data.description: Lowest Price Home in Bell Mountain:  Welcome to this stunning two-story home in Bell Mountain Ranch with Amazing Front Range Views. With 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a sprawling 3 car garage, this spacious home sits on over 4 acres of breathtaking land, providing an expansive playground for endless adventures. Step inside to discover an interior that combines elegance and practicality. The immaculate wood flooring can withstand the energy of an active lifestyle, while the oversized eat-in kitchen becomes the heart of the home. With slab exotic granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a double oven, and two dishwashers, preparing meals and hosting family cooking sessions becomes a joyous affair. The inviting great room, with its cozy fireplace, offers a comfortable gathering space for movie nights or board game marathons. For formal dinners and celebrations, a designated dining area provides a space to create lasting memories together. The private office offers a quiet retreat for manage household activities or work from home, while an additional living room can be transformed into a play area or space for imaginative adventures. Upstairs, the primary suite offers more beautiful views, a sitting area, an en-suite 5 piece bath and a walk-in closet with built-ins. Three additional spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets offer personal sanctuaries for each guest. The basement features a non-conforming bedroom with attached 3/4 bathroom plus a bonus room with a kitchenette, where your family can create a space for games, crafts, or hosting friends for poker nights. In this remarkable home, you can experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and outdoor adventures. Don't miss the opportunity to elevate your lifestyle and create lasting memories in this Bell Mountain Ranch gem.
